CapStar files to offer 5 mln shrs . CapStar Hotel Co said Wednesday it plans to file to offer five million shares of common stock . Net proceeds are to be used to pay for the cash portion of the purchase price of eight hotels it said it plans to acquire . The net proceeds also are to be used to retire outstanding balances under the company ' s credit facility and for general corporate purposes . The hotels are to be acquired in three separate transactions for $ 89 . 25 million in cash and $ 29 . 5 million in operating partnership units . 
